    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "Be careful not to use <code>Collections.reverse(List&lt;?&gt; list)</code> in a return statement expecting <code>List&lt;?&gt;</code> because : The Collections.reverse method <b>does not return a new list</b> ; instead, it <i>modifies the given list in place</i> and returns <b>void</b>. As a result, you cannot use it directly in a return statement."
  } ],
