      "post_id" : 3963075,
      "comment_id" : 140619543,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "I would recommend <code>Collections.reverse(new ArrayList&lt;&gt;(list))</code> or <code>Collections.reverse(List.copyOf(list))</code> (if no nulls) instead. This works regardless of whether the original list is cloneable, and is just as much of a shallow copy as <code>list.clone()</code>."
