    "body" : "<p>You can also do this: </p>\n\n<pre><code>static ArrayList&lt;String&gt; reverseReturn(ArrayList&lt;String&gt; alist)\n{\n   if(alist==null || alist.isEmpty())\n   { \n       return null;\n   }\n\n   ArrayList&lt;String&gt; rlist = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;(alist);\n\n   Collections.reverse(rlist);\n   return rlist;\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
