    "body" : "<p>Collections.reverse(nums) ... It actually reverse the order of the elements. \nBelow code should be much appreciated -</p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;Integer&gt; nums = new ArrayList&lt;Integer&gt;();\nnums.add(61);\nnums.add(42);\nnums.add(83);\nnums.add(94);\nnums.add(15);\n//Tosort the collections uncomment the below line\n//Collections.sort(nums); \n\nCollections.reverse(nums);\n\nSystem.out.println(nums);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Output: 15,94,83,42,61</p>\n"
